%% UML Activity (stateDiagram-v2 approximation) for attribute minimization flow.
stateDiagram-v2
    state "Receive requested attributes" as ReceiveRequest
    state "Validate requested attributes" as Validate
    state "Apply minimization policy<br>(selective disclosure where possible)" as ApplyMinimization
    state "Reject/Reduce over-request<br>and show warning" as RejectOrReduce
    state "Record privacy decision<br>(local audit)" as RecordDecision

    [*] --> ReceiveRequest
    ReceiveRequest --> Validate
    Validate --> ApplyMinimization: valid
    Validate --> RejectOrReduce: invalid/excessive
    ApplyMinimization --> RecordDecision
    RejectOrReduce --> RecordDecision
    RecordDecision --> [*]
